invalid type: string "\n# Statement of Work - Project Alpha Release v1.0\nDate: 2025-06-01\nStatus: APPROVED\n\n## Deliverables\n- Backend API (REST)\n- Mobile app (iOS + Android)\n- Dashboard UI\n- Documentation\n\n## Timeline\n- QA: June 1-15 (15% complete as of June 14)\n- UAT: June 16-20\n- Production Release: June 21\n\n## Budget\n- Total: $500,000\n- Spent: $420,000\n- Remaining: $80,000\n\n